Ahmed El-Fishawy (amụrụ na Nọvemba 11, 1980) bụ onye Egypt na-eme ihe nkiri na nwa nke onye Egypt a ma ama Farouk al-Fishaway.
Oge izizi o mere ihe nkiri bụ ya na Faten Hamama na usoro ihe nkiri Wajh al-Qamar
Mgbe ọ dị afọ iri abụọ na atọ, ọ pụtara na Afaret El Sayala (Ghosts of Sayala)
Ihe nkiri mbụ ya bụ El Hassa El Sab'aa

El-Fishawy alụọla nwanyị ugboro anọ, na-ejedebe na ịgba alụkwaghịm. Alụmdi na nwunye nzuzo ya na Hend El-Hennawi bụ ihe ihere mgbasa ozi na mmekọrịta mmadụ na ibe ya, n'ihi na ọ gọnahụrụ ịbụ nna nwa ha, Lina
E mechiri ikpe ahụ mgbe iwu ụlọ ikpe nyere maka nkwenye nna.
N'abalị iri abụọ na abụọ n'ọnwa Mee afọ 2018, ọ kwupụtara nkwa ịlụ Nada Kamel
Ha mere obere emume nzuzo n'ubọchị mbụ nke Mee.
N'ọnwa Nọvemba 2019, ụlọ ikpe mere mkpebi kwa afọ nke machibidoro Lina ime njem.
Na Jenụwarị 2020, a mara El-Fishawy ikpe ịga mkpọrọ otu afọ, n'ihi enweghị ike inye nkwado ụmụaka
Ikpe ahụ gụnyere otu afọ n'ụlọ mkpọrọ, mgbapụta nke £E 2,000, ịkwụ ụgwọ nke £E 500, na ịkwụ ụgwọ £E 20,000 na £E 50,000 maka ndị ọka iwu na mmefu ndị ọzọ.
